OL,3,CTV host 'sorry' for criticising player
OL,4,Cfor leaving World Cup for child's birth
OL,6,FA French TV presenter has apologised
OL,7,Fafter criticising Belgium player
OL,8,FJeremy Doku's decision to leave the
OL,9,FWorld Cup early to be with his wife
OL,10,Ffor the birth of their first child.
OL,12,FFrance Pierron, a presenter on the TV
OL,13,Fshow L'Equipe de Choc, sparked
OL,14,Fcriticism last week after she
OL,15,Fdescribed childbirth as "a disgusting
OL,16,Fmoment, excuse me, where the dad is
OL,17,Fuseless".
OL,26,@pD@BrrpD@DrruD@Hrb
