OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782173903
OL,3,CTV host 'sorry' for criticising player
OL,4,Cfor leaving World Cup for child's birth
OL,6,F"There are hundreds of footballers who
OL,7,Fwould kill to be in your place," she
OL,8,Fsaid of the Manchester City winger's
OL,9,Fdecision.
OL,11,FDoku announced last week he was going
OL,12,Fback home as his wife Shireen is due
OL,13,Fto give birth to their first child
OL,14,Fwhen Belgium hopes to be playing in
OL,15,Fthe knockout rounds of the World Cup.
OL,17,F"No one wants to miss a birth," the 24-
OL,18,Fyear-old player said.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@_O]
