OL,3,CTV host 'sorry' for criticising player
OL,4,Cfor leaving World Cup for child's birth
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FPierron questioned Doku's priorities,
OL,12,Farguing that he was "living a
OL,13,Fchildhood dream" and that the World
OL,14,FCup "might never happen again in your
OL,15,Flife".
OL,26,@tD@UOUwD@EO]
