PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782173903
OL,3,CTV host 'sorry' for criticising player
OL,4,Cfor leaving World Cup for child's birth
OL,6,FAfter her comments sparked anger
OL,7,Fonline, she apologised on social
OL,8,Fmedia, writing: "In light of the very
OL,9,Fnumerous reactions following my
OL,10,Fcomments... I wish to provide a few
OL,11,Fclarifications.
OL,13,F"In it, I expressed a personal
OL,14,Fopinion, within the framework of a
OL,15,Fdebate. In it, I was expressing a
OL,16,Fpersonal opinion, within the context
OL,17,Fof a contentious exchange.
OL,19,F"These remarks commit only me and in
OL,20,Fno way reflect a collective position.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
