PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782173903
OL,3,CTV host 'sorry' for criticising player
OL,4,Cfor leaving World Cup for child's birth
OL,6,F"I understand that they may have
OL,7,Fshocked, hurt, or wounded some of you,
OL,8,Fand I am sorry for that. My intention
OL,9,Fhas never been to minimise the place
OL,10,For role of fathers with their partner
OL,11,Fand their child."
OL,13,FFrench sports media leader L'Equipe
OL,14,Fhas disavowed the comments and also
OL,15,Fapologised to Doku in a statement late
OL,16,Fon Sunday, saying her comments did not
OL,17,Frepresent its values.
OL,26,@uD@^rb
