OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1782173903
OL,3,CTV host 'sorry' for criticising player
OL,4,Cfor leaving World Cup for child's birth
OL,6,FDoku received support from England
OL,7,Fforward Ollie Watkins, who was asked
OL,8,Fabout the family choices facing
OL,9,Fplayers.
OL,11,F"He said it only happens once, your
OL,12,Ffirst child. Welcoming them to the
OL,13,Fworld is a blessing," Watkins said
OL,14,Fduring a news conference at the
OL,15,FEngland training camp.
OL,17,F"Someone labeled it disgusting. And I
OL,18,Fthink for a start that's not a way to
OL,19,Flabel a birth. I don't think it's
OL,20,Fanyone else's business what he gets up
OL,21,Fto after training," Watkins added.
