OL,3,CTV host 'sorry' for criticising player
OL,4,Cfor leaving World Cup for child's birth
OL,6,FBelgium were held to a 0-0 draw by
OL,7,FIran in their second Group G match in
OL,8,FLos Angeles on Sunday.
OL,10,FThe star-studded Belgian side now face
OL,11,Fthe prospect of elimination at the
OL,12,Fearliest stage, having also drawn to
OL,13,FEgypt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
